name: Historic data (1908-1963) of benthic macrofauna from the Limfjord, Denmark
description: This historic benthic macrofauna dataset was digitizedandstandardized by ICES iintheframework of the EMODNet Biology project. It contains data from the DanishBiological Station who collected quantitative samples of the benthic macrofauna on a yearlybasis from a range of stations in the Limjord during more than 5 decades.
